SubjectRepublic of Namibia- Double Taxation Convention
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification the CONVENTION between CANADA and the with the REPUBLIC OF NAMIBIA FOR THE AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND ON CAPITAL.
